1\">{{cite book|author=Lauren Rosewarne|title=Part-time Perverts: Sex, Pop Culture, and Kink Management|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Ky_Y6KdIIBgC&pg=PA71|year=2011|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=978-0-313-39157-6|page=71}}</ref> Users uploading content select from a series of set categories. The most popular category, \"amateur\", tags 30% of all videos posted.<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://antonomase.fr/fi/mazieres_pornstudies_2014.pdf|page=85|doi=10.1080/23268743.2014.888214|title=Deep tags: toward a quantitative analysis of online pornography|journal=[[Porn Studies]] |volume=1|issue=1\u20132 |last1=Mazi\u00e8res|first1=Antoine |last2=Trachman|first2=Mathieu |last3=Cointet|first3=Jean-Philippe |last4=Coulmont|first4=Baptiste |last5=Prieur|first5=Christophe}}</ref> Popular gay uploads include \"big cocks\" and \"bare back\" with Oregon having the lowest gay porn view time at 1.5 hours a week while West Virginia has the highest view rate at 3.3 hours a week.<ref>{{cite web|title=Here's Everything You Need To Know About People's Gay Male Porn |url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/benhenry/year-of-the-daddy|publisher=Buzz Feed|accessdate=29 September 2017}}</ref> The proportion of female users amounts to 26% with increasing tendency.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Montgomery|first1=Sarah Jasmine|title='Porn for Women' Became Pornhub\u2019s Most Popular Search Term in 2017, So at Least There's That|url=https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2018/01/adult-film-site-women-men-statistics-2017|publisher=COMPLEX|accessdate=6 October 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Vitto|first1=Laura|title=Surprise: Women watched more porn in 2017|url=https://mashable.com/2018/01/09/porn-for-women-searches-2017/?europe=true#b1KNoRwu.OqR |publisher=Mashable |accessdate=6 October 2018}}</ref> In 2017, the website stated a 2.4% increase in women visitors with the most popular search term in the U.S. being \"Daddy\" and \"Mom\" worldwide.<ref>{{cite web|last1=O'Neill|first1=Natalie|title=Women are watching more