F Ferizaj|Ferizaj]]             | caps15=    | goals15 = \n| nationalyears1 =  | nationalteam1 = | nationalcaps1 =  | nationalgoals1 = \n| pcupdate = {{date|2020-04-10}}\n}}\n\n'''Mensur Idrizi''' ({{lang-mk|\u041c\u0435\u043d\u0441\u0443\u0440 \u0418\u0434\u0440\u0438\u0437\u0438}}) (born 3 August 1983) is a retired [[Striker (association football)|striker]] from the [[Republic of Macedonia]].\n\n==Club career==\nIdrizi is of [[Albanians in the Republic of Macedonia|Albanian]] ethnicity. A journeyman midfielder, he has played in Macedona, Albania and Kosovo.\n\n== Honours ==\n\n=== Sk\u00ebnderbeu Kor\u00e7\u00eb ===\n* [[Albanian Superliga]] (1): 2010-11\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.macedonianfootball.com Macedonian Football] {{in lang|en}}\n*{{soccerway|39732}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2011}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Idrizi, Mensur}}\n[[Category:1983 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Tetovo]]\n[[Category:Albanian footballers from North Macedonia]]\n[[Category:Association football wingers]]\n[[Category:Macedonian footballers]]\n[[Category:KF Shk\u00ebndija players]]\n[[Category:FK Rabotni\u010dki players]]\n[[Category:FK Vardar players]]\n[[Category:KF Elbasani players]]\n[[Category:KF Sk\u00ebnderbeu Kor\u00e7\u00eb players]]\n[[Category:FK Teteks players]]\n[[Category:KS Pogradeci players]]\n[[Category:FK Drita players]]\n[[Category:FK Renova players]]\n[[Category:KF Ferizaj players]]\n[[Category:Macedonian First Football League players]]\n[[Category:Macedonian Second Football League players]]\n[[Category:Albanian Superliga players]]\n[[Category:Football Superleague of Kosovo players]]\n[[Category:Macedonian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Albania]]\n[[Category:Macedonian expatriate sportspeople in Albania]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Kosovo]]\n[[Category:Macedonian expatriate sportspeople in Kosovo]]\n\n\n{{RMacedonia-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| 